<h2>Your Airport Transfer is Approved</h2>

<p>Hello {{name}},</p>

<p>Good news — your airport transfer request has been reviewed and approved.</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Airport:</strong> {{airport}}</li>
  <li><strong>Terminal:</strong> {{terminal}}</li>
  <li><strong>Date:</strong> {{formatDate date}}</li>
  <li><strong>Pickup Time:</strong> {{default pickupTime "To be confirmed"}}</li>
  <li><strong>Pickup Location:</strong> {{default pickupLocation "To be confirmed"}}</li>
  <li><strong>Vehicle:</strong> {{vehicle}}</li>
</ul>

<p>Our driver will be in touch ahead of your pickup time. If anything about your trip changes, please contact our team as soon as possible.</p>